@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About us";
}

<div>
     <h1>
         @ViewData["Title"]
     </h1>
    <p>
    <p>Welcome to Hello World Petshop, where we believe every pet deserves a little extra love and care!</p>
    <p>At Hello World Petshop, we’re more than just a pet store – we’re a family-run business dedicated to providing the very best for your furry, feathered, and scaly friends. Our journey began with a passion for animals and a dream to create a space where pet owners can find high-quality products and expert advice, all under one roof.</p>
    <p><strong>Our Mission</strong></p>
    <p>Our mission is simple: to enhance the lives of pets and their owners by offering top-notch products and personalized service. We understand that pets are family, and we’re committed to helping you give them the love and care they deserve. From nutritious food and engaging toys to comfortable bedding and grooming supplies, we strive to offer a curated selection of products that meet the highest standards of quality and safety.</p>
    <p><strong>What Sets Us Apart</strong></p>
    <ol>
        <li>
            <p><strong>Expert Staff</strong>: Our team is comprised of passionate pet lovers with extensive knowledge in animal care. Whether you need advice on pet nutrition, training tips, or product recommendations, we’re here to help.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <p><strong>Community Focused</strong>: We believe in giving back to the community that supports us. That’s why we partner with local shelters and rescue organizations to support pet adoption and welfare initiatives. When you shop with us, you’re also contributing to a cause that helps pets in need.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <p><strong>Quality Products</strong>: We carefully select each product we offer to ensure it meets our high standards. From premium pet foods to eco-friendly toys, we’re committed to offering items that are safe, effective, and enjoyable for your pets.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <p><strong>Personalized Service</strong>: Every pet is unique, and so are their needs. Our staff takes the time to understand your pet’s specific requirements and preferences to provide tailored recommendations that work best for you and your furry friend.</p>
        </li>
    </ol>
    <p><strong>Our Store</strong></p>
    <p>Our store is designed to be a welcoming and enjoyable space for both pets and their owners. You’ll find everything you need for your pets, and you might even make a few new furry friends along the way! We also offer special events and workshops to help you stay informed and connected with other pet enthusiasts.</p>
    <p><strong>Join Our Pet-Loving Community</strong></p>
    <p>We invite you to visit us and experience the Hello World Petshop difference for yourself. Follow us on social media and subscribe to our newsletter for the latest updates, special offers, and pet care tips.</p>
    <p>Thank you for choosing Hello World Petshop – where every pet is a part of our family!</p>
    <p>
        With paws and whiskers,
        The Hello World Petshop Team
    </p>

    </p>
</div>